{
  "stem": "25773.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if I'd ever survive, I'll never return to this damned place-- a damned place, never [? is there. ?] And I-- you can imagine in my heart how I was listening to this story that the-- and the-- and the burning wind was bringing even smells sometimes from the-- from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The ghetto was burning forever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because it was like 1920-- in Ap-- April, 1943, was the Jewish upraising.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a very heroic thing-- a few people there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They did a lot of damage to the tanks, to the German tanks, and to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But eventually, they had like-- like in Masada, they had-- they committed suicide, by [? running ?] down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyway, this cousin of mine invited this German director.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was shivering, absolutely, from fright.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he was not afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He invited him for a weekend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He invited him for the weekend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they-- it didn't occur to the German that I could be Jewish, looking after the little girl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, in the-- this-- during the day, they went to a place for either fishing, or the boat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They brought in a big bucket of little crabs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they brought it home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my cousin was supposed to cook it the next day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In Poland, you used to eat a lot of these crabs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was sleeping in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That was my place.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in the night, I got up, for one reason or the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And suddenly, I saw that the whole floor was walking!",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The whole floor was walking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was completely-- I have realized that they didn't cover these crabs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they made their way all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It was a frightening experience-- funny and awful.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
